"title": "8262: generosity, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8262",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Believers should be generous in their dealings with others, following the example of God himself.</p>\n<h2>Motivations for generosity</h2>\n<h3>God's example</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7-2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:7–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16-1John3:18\">1JN 3:16–3:18</a></p>\n<h3>God's dealings with believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32-Eph5:2\">EPH 4:32–5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:7-Matt10:8\">MAT 10:7–10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a></p>\n<h2>Demonstrations of generosity</h2>\n<h3>In material giving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:32–4:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:35\">LEV 25:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7-Deut15:8\">DEU 15:7–15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:42\">MAT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:3\">2CO 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:5\">2CO 9:5</a></p>\n<h3>In support of God's work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:16\">PHP 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:5\">EXO 36:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:13-Num7:17\">NUM 7:13–7:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:14-1Chr28:18\">1CH 28:14–28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:9-2Chr31:10\">2CH 31:9–31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">MRK 12:41–12:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:17–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>In worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:6-Matt26:7\">MAT 26:6–26:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:4\">1KI 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:63\">1KI 8:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:6\">2CH 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:6\">2CH 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:9\">EZR 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:17\">PHP 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>In acts of mercy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:33-Luke10:35\">LUK 10:33–10:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:22\">2KI 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:15\">2CH 28:15</a></p>\n<h3>In giving presents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:13\">1KI 10:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:53\">GEN 24:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:17-Gen32:21\">GEN 32:17–32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:21-Gen45:23\">GEN 45:21–45:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:5\">2KI 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:9\">2KI 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>Meanness and covetousness the opposites of generosity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:13\">ECC 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:2-2Sam12:4\">2SA 12:2–12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:23-Isa43:24\">ISA 43:23–43:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:2\">MIC 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:8-Mal3:9\">MAL 3:8–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:45\">MAT 25:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a></p>\n<h2>Generosity rewarded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25-Ps37:26\">PSA 37:25–37:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:5\">PSA 112:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:9\">PSA 112:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:24-Prov11:25\">PRO 11:24–11:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:9\">PRO 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:10\">ISA 58:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:38\">LUK 6:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6-2Cor9:9\">2CO 9:6–9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:9-Gal6:10\">GAL 6:9–6:10</a></p>",
